  "update_count": 52,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nDiscardsGraphDumpImpl::StartFrameFaviconRequest() will post a task to UIThreadTaskRunner, and then call FaviconRequestHelper::RequestFavicon()[1], using raw pointer returned from EnsureFaviconRequestHelper()[2]. DiscardsGraphDumpImpl owns FaviconRequestHelper instance[3]"
